00:21:15.000 --> 00:21:16.310
Kami, Pengawal Feiyu, bertindak
atas perintah kekaisaran.

00:21:16.310 --> 00:21:17.160
Mereka yang berani membangkang

00:21:17.160 --> 00:21:19.480
